{"tid":697880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（捐錢啦淨係識呃like）抗爭惹上官非 被告盧建民慨嘆生活淒慘","createTime":"2018-06-11T08:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T04:27:55.000Z","uid":51129,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9f6b9cc5de2dee06e9a538d6bf8f9d4e58eb25f3","tid":697880,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T08:52:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180518/2_585907_0/-%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%84%E5%89%8D%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E6%83%B9%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%98%E9%9D%9E-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E6%85%A8%E5%98%86%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%B7%92%E6%85%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180518%2F2_585907_0%2F-%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%258D%2584%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%2583%25B9%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25AE%2598%25E9%259D%259E-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%2585%25A8%25E5%2598%2586%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E6%25B7%2592%25E6%2585%2598&d=GbEA7B6eLkiPEXlQfMrUt9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=053787c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180518%2F2_585907_0%2F-%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%258D%2584%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%2583%25B9%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25AE%2598%25E9%259D%259E-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%2585%25A8%25E5%2598%2586%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E6%25B7%2592%25E6%2585%2598&h=5620cd6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180518/2_585907_0/-%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%84%E5%89%8D%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E6%83%B9%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%98%E9%9D%9E-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E6%85%A8%E5%98%86%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%B7%92%E6%85%98</a><br />\n<br />\n旺角騷亂案被告一盧建民，他被 裁定 暴動罪成立。 <br />\n<br />\n他早前接受本刊專訪時承認，自旺角騷亂事件後，原本激進抗爭的一群，也沉寂下來了，「是低沉了，沒有辦法，有些被人控告，有些被拘捕，有些又在監獄，還會有什麼人。」他又說，會擔心警察會上他家，騷擾到家人，「所以現在我也不敢回去住，自己搬了出來，(住劏房？)，住太空倉，是太空倉。」 <br />\n<br />\n自這件事後，他坦言自己生活淒慘，「都慘的，因為這官司，要住太空倉，又不能回家住，連工作也未必找到。所以要靠人接濟，朋友或政府援助，正在拿取政府援助。」生活上，是拮据的。 <br />\n<br />\n因為他們都是寂寂無名的一群，事後沒有任何人幫他們，「我們這些沒有政黨幫助的，因為我們被定性為激進的，沒有政黨肯幫我們。 加上我們不是梁天琦，他就有很多人幫手，我們沒有的。 」 <br />\n<br />\n沒有工作，生活上要十分慳儉，「一個月四千元(援助)，一個月有四千元用，交完屋租後慳一點。(屋租多少錢？)太空倉二千多元，慳一點便可以。」"},{"pid":"6c2e82da54e37ea98ebef1a5de90846d1539904d","tid":697880,"uid":3454,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T08:53:21.000Z","msg":"20180518<br />\n<br />\n5毛群龍共舞又回帶舊聞"},{"pid":"d8170aa76a35c23aed47b09e3043b30a274506f3","tid":697880,"uid":51129,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T08:53:23.000Z","msg":"cc台班淨係識正皮鍵國嗰千幾條廢柴，你地捐咗幾多錢俾義士呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟作為五毛代表，就小小地捐咗300蚊咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多位鍵國勇士唔一人捐返千幾二千好似說不過去喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/164336_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F164336_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b0b3eb3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/152631_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F152631_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=fbd8e919&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n捐款details：<br />\n<br />\n[集氣籌旗]請各位捐錢畀星火轉交義士, 我都捐咗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/671388/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/671388/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"8d22abd193da7104bc621adb455d3dc0c7bf3b86","tid":697880,"uid":51129,